      <p>
        The data above is divided in to two main parts. The location section has meta information like local time, timezone as well as latitude and longitude.
        The bulk of the weather data is contained within the current section. The data fields are fairly self explanatory, with the exception of the condition field.
        The condition section is used to inform users what corresponding icon should be shown along with the weather information.
      </p>
